plot: Mr. Peanutbutter's posh campaign fundraiser takes a terrifying turn. As chaos swirls around them. BoJack and Diane get drunk.

Mr. Peanut Butter and Woodchuck vie for power over the celebrity guests of a fundraising event, which degenerates into chaos when the guests become trapped in Mr. Peanut Butter's house when it collapses into the underground. Meanwhile, Todd and Princess Carolyn represent a collection of worker ant people they encounter while searching for an escape route and BoJack and Diane reconnect over hoarded alcohol from the party.—patricio-53898
